{
  "texts": [
    "In pre-learning, BERT identifies many redundant words to complete the representation.",
    "The tasks adopted in this study include multilayer masking (MLM) and next-sentence prediction (NSP).",
    "MLM improves the understanding of past and future content by clarifying a set of input tokens and training a model to predict the original tokens [93].",
    "BERT influences NSP technology to improve understanding of relationships by analyzing whether the second expression follows the first expression.",
    "The BERT system uses data annotations to focus on specific tasks later in the initial training session."
  ]
}